{"tid":1489472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter封鎖逾20萬個賬戶，相信那些賬戶與中國政府有關","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:13.000Z","uid":156878,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a52ba58a8d94a8014cc0e0c4a62e5203100ef88","tid":1489472,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Well done<br />\n<br />\n社交網站Twitter和facebook周一指中國利用大量假賬戶散播假資訊，「散播政治不和」，試圖打擊香港因「反送中」而起的示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報道，Twitter封鎖逾20萬個賬戶，相信那些賬戶與中國政府有關，涉及針對香港示威的散播假新聞行動，那些賬戶將香港示威者描繪成「不代表香港大多數人的罪犯」。美聯社引述Twitter一名高層表示，這次行動主要由三個冒充駐港新聞機構的中英文賬戶發動，目的將示威者描繪為暴徒，影響輿論。這名高層表示，那些賬戶違反Twitter服務條款，所以予以封鎖，並表示已將中國這些活動向聯邦調查局（FBI）報告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter周一在網誌帖文寫道，其中936個被封賬戶「最為活躍」，蓄意而明確地企圖在香港挑撥離間，指這些活動「有國家支持，而且互相配合」。Twitter指出，那些賬戶「暗中破壞香港示威活動的合法性與政治立場」。"},{"pid":"2563ab230766cba410d2b6694c7f68edcb19edbc","tid":1489472,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"GJ<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投資國難五金發國難財Ver 2.0</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1eb13a66a1a34b887d8da0e504d77cc84436f9f3","tid":1489472,"uid":186176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSxwzi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSxwzi0.png&h=c67dd9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70737eacfe9b8fdef53210c0fd1c761557577584","tid":1489472,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e68e9d849dac7fb0e2e8fb039dc1fa0a62b307b2","tid":1489472,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}